snippet.title: WBSC eBaseball: Power Pros (PS4) - Gameplay
snippet.description:
A five-inning online quick match from the new Power Pros game just released this week for PS4 and Switch. 

Normal ranked online matches are three innings, for what it’s worth. This is one of the “quick games” that can be any length you choose.

I also have a page for the game on my Baseball Video Game Encyclopedia at 30-30.club: https://30-30.club/wiki/wbsc-ebaseball-power-pros/
